VALUES (84, 'Spiderman Push Up Video Exercise Guide', 'Chest', 'Strength', 'Bodyweight', 'Compound', 'Push (Bilateral)',
        'Intermediate', 'Abs, Shoulders, Triceps', 'The Spiderman push up is a combination movement and a variation of the push up. It combines the push up exercise with a hip flexion to target the pushing muscles of the upper body as well as the core.
